        <title>POWER STEERING OIL COOLER</title>
        <para>The power steering oil cooler is available as an option on the ProStar&#8482; for trucks that are utilized
            in several conditions. The power steering oil cooler is a tube designed oil cooler that oil passes through
            and it provides an efficient way to remove heat from the power steering fluid.
        </para>
